Notes on building Ruby Gem to list Charles' De lints- New books Books and details

1. Plan your gem, imagine your interface [x]
2. Start with e project structure- google [x]
3. Start with the entry point - the file run [x]
4. force that to build the CLI interface [x]
5. stub out the interface
6. start making things real
7. discover objects
8. program

User can list books
This Gem will allow a user to input a list number of a book to get small description

The CLI will output book title and ask if user would like more information

